name: PetsNa
description: Welcome to the Cosplay Husky Memeverse, where one derpy husky, a suitcase of costumes, and the power of decentralized memes collide to birth the most chaotic, culturally contagious, crypto-native movement the internet has seen since Doge said “Wow”. A husky memecoin born from TikTok chaos. One dog. One million outfits. One token to meme them all. Nope. Doge walked so PetsNa could strut in cosplay. This husky wears capes, not collars.
